\par\pard\plain \ltrch\loch {\f0\fs24\b1 Thought 1}{\f0\fs24 . The way to overcome the fears and disappointments of life is to hear and believe God\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s Word, His wonderful promise to give us }{\f0\fs24\i1 the promised land}{\f0\fs24 , to give us heaven itself. This is the very reason God saves us, to give us the promised land of heaven, the glorious hope of living together in fellowship with Him forever and ever. This hope\hich\f0 \emdash \loch\f0 the hope of heaven\hich\f0 \emdash \loch\f0 helps to erase fear and disappointment. For we know that whatever happens to us\hich\f0 \emdash \loch\f0 even if someone kills our bodies\hich\f0 \emdash \loch\f0 our souls will live on and on forever with God.\{\\Scrv_fn=}{\f2\fs24\b0\i0  Leadership Ministries Worldwide. (1996). \\end_Scrv_fn\}\{\\Scrv_fn=}{\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "https://ref.ly/logosres/posbkjv01ge2?ref=Bible.Ge15.7-21&off=7387&ctx=m+II+(2+K.+14:25).2%0a~Thought+1.+The+way+t"}{\fldrslt\f3\fs24\b0\i1\ul\ulc0\cf3 Genesis (Chapters 12\endash 50)\\end_Scrv_fn\}\{\\Scrv_fn=}}{\f2\fs24\b0\i0  (Vol. II, p. 69). Chattanooga, TN: Leadership Ministries Worldwide.\\end_Scrv_fn\}}
